/*********************************************************************
* Function:  void ExitSleepMode (void)
* PreCondition: none
* Input:  none
* Output: none
* Side Effects: none
* Overview: SSD1963 exits sleep mode
* Note:   cannot be called sooner than 15ms
********************************************************************/
void ExitSleepMode (void);

